blogPost.excerpt: The fastest human footspeed was recorded by Usain Bolt at 27.8mph. Recently I broke that record.
blogPost.body: The fastest human footspeed was recorded by Usain Bolt at 27.8mph. Recently I broke that record.

blogPost.author: Remi B

localize.title: 世界纪录！人类有史以来最快的脚步速度!
